<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5536827>
    dc:description "Fig. 149. Sarax stygochthobius(Weygoldt &Van Damme, 2004) comb.nov.(HLMD EA–172–HT), general morphology, ♂. A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. Sternum, ventral view. C. Frontal process. D. Pedipalp, dorsal view. F. Pedipalp, ventral view. Scale bars: A–B, D–E = 1 mm; C = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5536827/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5536796>
    dc:description "Fig. 141. Sarax cochinensis (Gravely, 1915) (AMCC [LP 13118]), general morphology, ♀. A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. Sternum, ventral view. C. Frontal process. D. Pedipalp tarsus, frontal view. E. Pedipalp, dorsal view. F. Pedipalp, ventral view. Scale bars: A–B, E–F = 1 mm; C = 0.1 mm; D = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5536796/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5536820>
    dc:description "Fig. 148. Sarax socotranus (Weygoldt, Pohl & Polak, 2002) comb. nov. (HLMD EA-45-HT), general morphology, ♂. A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. Sternum, ventral view. C. Frontal process. D. Pedipalp, dorsal view. F. Pedipalp, ventral view. Scale bars: A–B, D–E = 1 mm; C = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5536820/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5536778>
    dc:description "Fig. 136. Sarax abbatei (Delle Cave, 1986) comb. nov. (MZUF 1896–167), general morphology, ♀. A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. Sternum, ventral view. C. Frontal process. D. Pedipalp tarsus, frontal view. E. Pedipalp, dorsal view. F. Pedipalp, ventral view. Scale bars: A, E–F = 1 mm; B–D = 0.1 mm." ;
