<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5536806>
    dc:description "Fig. 144. Sarax pakistanus (Weygoldt, 2005) comb. nov. (MHNG), general morphology,♂. A. Carapace, dorsal view. B. Sternum, ventral view. C. Frontal process. D. Pedipalp tarsus, frontal view. E. Pedipalp, dorsal view. F. Pedipalp, ventral view. Scale bars: A–B, E–F = 1 mm; C = 0.1 mm; D = 0.5 mm." ;
